No. 905,

Mise;

Whitney v. Florida. Petitioner pro se. Earl Faircloth, Attorney General of Florida, and James T. Carlisle, Assistant Attorney General, for respondent.

Dist. Ct. App. Fla., 3d Dist. Motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis and petition for writ of certiorari granted. Case transferred to appellate docket.
